            <title>[LU-4664] sync write should consume grant on client</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4664</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Sync/direct write should consume grant on client as well, otherwise, it could fail with ENOSPC even when there is lots of grant reserved by clients.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
